'''Nnamdi Ezeigbo''' (born August 4, 1966, from Nsukwe, [[Ubakala]] [[Umuahia]], [[Abia State]]) is a Nigerian entrepreneur. He is the [[Chief executive officer]] of Slot Systems Limited.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://encomium.ng/the-inspiring-story-of-how-slots-founder-nnamdi-ezeigbo-became-a-billionaire/|title=The inspiring story of how Slot’s founder, Nnamdi Ezeigbo became a billionaire!|work=Encomium Magazine|access-date=2017-11-26|language=en-US}}</ref>
In 2014, he was awarded with the Nigeria Entrepreneurs Award For Excellent & Business Innovation.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.entrepreneursaward.com/past-participants-2014.html|title=Nigeria Entrepreneur Awards: 2017 Awards|website=www.entrepreneursaward.com|access-date=2017-11-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://enterprise54.com/finally-nominations-are-out-for-the-nigeria-entrepreneurs-awards-2015/|title=Finally, Nominations are out for the Nigeria Entrepreneurs Awards 2015 - The Website for African Entrepreneurs|date=2015-09-07|work=The Website for African Entrepreneurs|access-date=2017-11-26|language=en-US}}</ref>
